title[47]='MAINTENANCE';
contents[47]='MAINTENANCE';

urlHash[48]='section_10';
title[48]='Cleaning';
contents[48]='CleaningBefore cleaning or performing maintenance, disconnect the power supply and wait until the fan stops.Check the air filter at least twice a month to see if cleaning is necessary. Trapped particles in the filter can build up and block the airflow, reducing cooling capacity and causing an accumulation of frost on the evaporator.';
